@startuml
!include common-sequence.iuml

title delete-func-api-ota-get\n(GitHub Action → CloudFormation)

actor "GitHub Actions Runner" as GHA

box "AWS" #ffdbbb
    participant "CloudFormation / SAM" as CF
    participant "SSM Parameter Store" as SSM
    participant "API Gateway" as APIGW
end box

GHA -> CF++ : SAM delete\nstack: firefly-func-api-ota-get
CF -> APIGW : Remove route\nGET /ota/{product_id}/{application}
CF --> GHA-- : DELETE_COMPLETE

note over SSM : FIRMWARE_TYPE_MAP SSM parameter\nis NOT deleted automatically.\nManual cleanup required for\nfull environment teardown.

@enduml
